							<h4>22.04.24</h4>
							<h1>Avoiding the Legacy Trap: Strategies to Maintain Cutting-Edge Software</h1>
						</div>
						
					</div>
					
					<div class="row aos-init aos-animate" data-aos="fade-down">

						<div class="wrap-content larger thumbnail-wrap">
							
							<div class="over-cats">
															</div>
							
